about: Lumenare Networks develops solutions for lab automation and test management. Its solutions automate manual steps in the pre-production testing of new network services, infrastructure upgrades, or network devices. The company’s software provides automation at various steps of the testing lifecycle, including asset discovery, configuration, reservation, test scheduling, topology creation, resource planning, and reporting. Its software is in use by service providers, enterprises, service area network providers, and network equipment manufacturers to accelerate time-to-market for new products and services. The company offers TestExpert software that accelerates test planning, development, execution, archiving, and reporting using a common database; and LabMagic software that meets lab testing requirements for inventory control, configuration management, resource scheduling, and connectivity management

about: Riverbend Meats is a family owned beef processing company with a new, state-of-the-art processing facility dedicated to providing superior quality beef to consumers throughout the United States. Riverbend owns and manages the cattle, ranch land, feed lots and, its own processing facilities. That makes it the only American beef processor of its size that owns and manages 100% of its own beef from birth to harvest. Riverbend Ranch is considered one of the leading purebred Angus operations in the nation. Riverbend focus on quality Angus beef and its new, state-of-the-art processing facility positions it as a premier provider of quality beef. Riverbend Meats’ focuses on all-natural, hormone free beef that has never been fed or treated with antibiotics. This produces a superior and healthier beef option for the educated consumer. Riverbend is also known for its ethical livestock management and its protection of the environment. Such an offering creates high demand for Riverbend Meats for those who are health minded and who care about where their beef comes from and how it has been treated during his lifetime. Riverbend provides lucrative pay and great job opportunities for those who are seeking careers in beef processing.

about: REGRIP: Pioneering a Sustainable Solution for a Cleaner World In a world that generates an astonishing 1.5 billion discarded tires annually, the environmental impact cannot be understated. Shockingly, only a mere 20% of these tires find their way to recycling facilities, leaving a staggering 80% to languish in landfills for hundreds of years, wreaking havoc on our environment and health. It's a challenge that calls for innovative solutions, and that's precisely where REGRIP steps in. At REGRIP, we are committed to addressing this global tire crisis head-on by embracing the principles of the circular economy within the tire industry. Our mission is clear: to breathe new life into discarded tires, extending their usefulness and minimizing their adverse effects on the planet. We accomplish this in two crucial ways: Maximizing Tire End Life: Instead of allowing tires to become waste prematurely, we employ advanced techniques and technologies to make them reusable once more. This not only conserves valuable resources but also extends the lifespan of each tire, reducing the need for new tire production and minimizing the environmental footprint. Converting Non-Reusable Tires into Raw Materials: For tires that have reached the end of their usable life, we take an eco-friendly approach. By transforming these non-reusable tires into valuable raw materials, we ensure they are efficiently removed from the environment, mitigating the pollution and harm they would otherwise cause. At REGRIP, we are dedicated to driving change in the tire industry, moving it towards a more sustainable and responsible future. By redefining the fate of discarded tires and embracing a circular economy mindset, we are not only reducing pollution but also contributing to the well-being of both the environment and humanity. Join us on our mission to create a cleaner, greener world, one tire at a time. Together, we can make a profound impact and pave the way for a more sustainable future.

about: SalarySe is a salary powered fintech platform that is redefining the landscape of financial services in India for the 10 Crore salaried individuals earning $300bn+ per year. We focus on lower to middle-class salaried employees constituting ~60% of the salaried income pool in India with a mission to enable seamless UPI - credit - rewards experience at best-on-street prices and convenience. SalarySe provides revolving credit on UPI by integrating with payroll systems of companies and uses a lien on salary for repayments as a lever to reduce credit risk. about: HRK GROUP ECO-FRIENDLY PACKAGING AND SINGLE USE ITEMS SPECIALIST HRK import export and distribution company started in 2019 with the goal to offer real eco-friendly alternatives to plastic packaging and single use items. Over 150,000,000 tons of plastic packaging and single use items are produced each year and with less than 10% being recycled they are a huge contributor to the plastic waste crisis. Our solutions are suitable for a large range of industries. All our products are designed to reach the highest quality and environment friendly standards. With this unique combination, we are able to replace harmful plastics with practical products that offer great technical properties and perform as good and sometimes even better. We have made successful collaboration in the manufacturing industry, food processing, retail industry, garment industry, farming industry, hospitality, health care sector and more Dealing with eco-friendly plastics brings a lot of questions regarding the authenticity of their environment friendly claims. This is why to guarantee the quality of our products we invested in two factories to make sure our products are at the highest standards and we are now leading the way in Vietnam for unique eco-friendly innovations: GPS PLAS factory is a pioneer in the development of biodegradable and compostable resins in Vietnam with many unique innovations in flexible film packaging. PVA PRO is the first factory in Vietnam to manufacture water soluble PVA resin and flexible film packaging to deliver one more high-tech eco-friendly solution. Contact us: contact@hrk-group.com www.hrk-group.com

about: Swizcom Technologies India Pvt Ltd is a world-class product engineering and software consulting company headquartered in Bangalore, India. The company was founded in 2011 and has been active in the US, Asia-Pacific and GCC countries since then. In 2012, Swizcom forayed into healthcare, by developing an outstanding Hospital Information Management System (HIMS) called ‘MediSwiz’. MediSwiz is comprehensive hospital-wide workflow based information system, which covers all aspects of hospital management and day-to-day operations of a hospital. It is a completely web-based system that caters to the needs of hospitals and is designed to manage and improve clinical, administrative, financial, inventory and other operational aspects to provide better patient care with its 24 modules. Swizcom also offers a complete cloud -based Quality Management Solution (QMS) that enables health care facilities to follow the quality management processes and their efforts towards quality standards or accreditation. Over the years we have developed a wide set of competencies and a proven global delivery model. This enables us to be the perfect partner of global firms in their outsourcing initiatives.Swizcom believes in delivering the best quality services and support to its clients. As experts in the design and development of software systems, we offer continual support from implementation through completion. Our team also provides software services for different verticals in various industries through technology stacks such as Java, J2EE, JSF, Hibernate, Spring, Groovy on Grails, Liferay, Angular JS, Bootstrap, Restful Web services and BPM engines such as jBPM, activiti, etc. Having the commitment, passion and dedication to excel we also strive hard to offer the best value propositions to our customers in an accountable and reliable way.

about: Fresco Logic was founded by a team of industry veterans that has worked together for over two decades at many leading technology companies including Intel, Cascade Semiconductor Solutions and Synopsys. Fresco Logic is first to market with USB3.0 Host and Device solutions, and demonstrated the world's first USB3.0 real time data transfer on its FPGA development platform in August 19-21, 2008 at the Intel Developer Forum (IDF). For almost two decades, the key members of the Fresco Team were actively involved in and participated in many technological changes in the computer I/O interconnect and networking fields, including directly contributing to the success of fast Ethernet, Gigabit Ethernet, InfiniBand and PCI Express. The Fresco team has a proven track record of delivering the industry’s first and best products in many key technologies such as PCI Express, Ethernet, InfiniBand, USB, Fibre Channels, and Wi-FI. Fresco Logic is headquartered in Beaverton, Oregon, with branch a office and design center in Neihu Science Park in Taipei Taiwan.

about: At EG427 our unique, non-replicative Herpes Simplex Virus type 1 (HSV-1) based vector platform delivers, with pinpoint precision, highly selective, durable expression of disease modifying transgenes for use in the treatment of peripheral nervous system disorders and beyond. Our lead asset EG110A, for the treatment of neurogenic bladder dysfunction, is expected to be in the clinic by early 2024. Our revolutionary approach to the treatment of this disease aims at providing patients with a comprehensive, long-term solution to their bladder management, through a highly selective molecular biology approach overcoming the drawbacks of current standard of care. Our HQ and labs are in Paris, France, where we were founded in 2019. We have raised over USD 15 million, including from our Series A in 2021.

about: 9th Gear enables the deployment of liquidity to achieve near instant and simultaneous settlement. Now is the time to implement market structures that offer real-time settlement, reduced risk, and lowered cost coupled with intraday liquidity. 9th Gear’s platform allows digital assets to be tracked through tokens created on its private permissioned blockchain (a proprietary and immutable digital ledger). In the case of foreign exchange and payments, tokens take the form of synthetic digital currency that can be traded and re-traded within the closed ecosystem. The platform’s unique design can be applied to many other product lines and across different asset classes to track liquidity and collateral, respectively. The platform is API and AWS message queue enabled for easy connection to multiple, disparate systems. The digital solution improves the transparency of transactions, increases investor confidence and demonstrates fair treatment of all market participants.

about: Bajío is the Spanish word for the shallows, that magical part of the ocean between land and the deep blue. The shoals, the reefs, the flats that lie just under the surface. The connection zone, teeming with life. These shallows are the world in which we are deeply rooted and from where we draw our inspiration. We believe in fishing. In its power to bring people together. We build sunglasses for those who fish. Who cast, drift, strip and set. Who prowl the waters where bonefish tail. Tarpon roll. Barracuda lie in wait. Where Redfish eat, nose down. Where Rainbows sip and big browns lurk in lairs. And where Billfish explode amidst screams of “marlin, marlin!!” We believe that the way you see the world impacts how you feel about it. We are driven to find the latest technologies and manufacturing techniques to create the most powerful visual experiences possible. We are driven to create products that are ocean-friendly, and to use clean manufacturing and green energy in our production. We believe in taking a human approach to business. We believe it’s important to treat people as people.

about: TotalTrax, Inc. is the leading provider of real time vehicle, driver and inventory tracking technologies for manufacturing and warehouse operations. Offering a complete technology platform that transforms traditional material handling vehicles into “smart trucks”, TotalTrax provides solutions that automate data collection and reporting for materials handling operations. With patented hardware, software, reporting and business intelligence tools, TotalTrax delivers substantial value in safety, fleet utilization, labor productivity and inventory accuracy. By automating vehicle usage, maintenance, impacts and lift truck load and location visibility data, customers are able to reduce or eliminate the inaccuracies normally associated with operator input. about: We want to reimagine TV. Zenterio enables TV Operators to securely and efficiently manage and deliver entertainment to the home while increasing business insight and value. Zenterio’s portfolio of products and solutions includes a complete TV and OTT entertainment experience client. In addition, Zenterio provides cloud-based solutions for content aggregation, data and analytics, home automation integrations and advanced advertising capabilities with a focus on reducing cost and increasing ARPU. Zenterio also provides professional and consulting services, with global partners, to provide future-proofed lifecycle management for Linux and Android platforms. Our offices are in Linköping, Atlanta and Dublin. We are owned by private investors and the private equity firm Scope. The Chairman of the Board is former Nokia CEO Olli-Pekka Kallasvuo and the CEO is former Ericsson executive Jorgen Nilsson.

about: 上海派森诺生物科技有限公司（以下简称“派森诺生物”）成立于2011年4月，旗下设有全资子公司-上海桑尼生物科技有限公司。派森诺生物以上海交通大学等海内外高等学校和科研院所的专家教授团队为技术依托，吸纳了多名基因组学和生物信息学高级专业技术人员加盟，是一家集科技服务、健康检测、产品研发为一体的国内知名企业。 公司之所以取名派森诺生物（Personalbio）是这样考虑的：首先，人类基因组计划实施和完成，全面开启了生命科学新纪元，其正带动着生物科学研究和应用进入个性化时代；其次，测序技术的飞速发展，以测序中心独揽天下的局面也将被以实验室为单位个性化形式所打破和取代。另外，由于生物种类和客户需求目标的多样性，要求有针对性、个性化的专业服务。 派森诺生物总部位于上海市徐汇区，目前已在国内10多个省市设立办事机构，合作伙伴遍布全国。公司拥有Roche 454 FLX+、Illumina MiSeq、Illumina HiSeq 2500、Illumina NextSeq 500、Ion Proton等最新款高通量测序平台和相关仪器设备，同时拥有一支高水平的基因测序合成、新产品研发和生物信息分析团队。公司致力于为生物、农业、医药、环境等领域研究人员提供动物、植物和微生物样品提取检测、文库构建、序列测序、生物信息分析和指导文章写作等一站式服务。 派森诺生物始终以“解析序列，诠释生命”作为企业理念，秉承“立足客户需要，满足个性需求”的服务宗旨，一如既往地致力于为广大合作伙伴提供高品质、高效率的技术服务，并提供三大免费服务：免费设计科学合理的实验方案、免费提供常规生物信息分析和免费修改润色英文文稿。 公司合作伙伴遍布全国，包括中国科学院、中国农业科学院、国家海洋局第一海洋研究所、中国水产研究院、清华大学深圳研究生院、上海交通大学、重庆市畜牧科学院、华东理工大学、南京大学、内蒙古农业大学、华中农业大学、华南农业大学、上海海洋大学、山东农业大学、扬州大学、温州医学院、瑞金医院、新华医院、华山医院、肿瘤医院、仁济医院等，已经完成和正在进行多项国家和省市重大或重点科研项目，受到合作伙伴的认同和好评。

about: Nido Bio is translating today’s neuroscience breakthroughs into tomorrow’s treatments for severe neurological diseases. Leveraging human genetics, we develop precision medicines that address the fundamental biology of disease and restore healthy cell function. NIDO-361, our clinical-stage candidate, is a treatment for Spinal and Bulbar Muscular Atrophy which is a rare and debilitating neuromuscular disease. Additional pipeline programs center around a novel target with the potential to address multiple disease mechanisms and that has broad clinical application across neurodegenerative and peripheral inflammatory diseases. We are creating a sustainable pipeline for the company by utilizing a functional genomics discovery platform based on human cell lines to identify novel targets. Through our approach we seek to transform patient lives in meaningful ways. www.nidobio.com.

about: From a leather studio on Haight Street, founded in 1967, Circa grew into a 100,000 square foot modern facility in the The Bayview. The domestic factory was home to the most current and innovative machinery, and our client relationships were longstanding, with best-in-class service. Private Equity acquired majority ownership in 2016, and drove this vibrant business into bankruptcy by 2020, disregarding the cost to employees, vendors, and clients along the way. A few of the long-time team members are working to bring a new, brand-focused design and manufacturing service to the market with an updated business model. If you are interested in leveraging factory direct pricing and attention to the unique needs the modern retail environment, stay tuned for updates! For immediate inquiries, please contact info@circasf.com.

about: PandaLab, Découvrez aujourd'hui la médecine de demain ! PandaLab réinvente la coordination en santé en proposant une solution complète de e-santé destinée à tous les professionnels acteurs de la prise en charge du patient. PandaLab est le meilleur moyen de communiquer dans, entre et autour des établissements de santé. Notre vocation est d'améliorer la communication pour réduire le nombre d'erreurs liées aux soins et d'offrir tous les outils nécessaires à une pratique médicale quotidienne plus fluide. Rapide, fiable et mobile, la messagerie permet d’envoyer en un éclair toutes les informations, comptes rendus et fichiers dont vous avez besoin pour la prise en charge de vos patients. Les fonctionnalités médicales intégrées vous garantissent un gain de temps considérable chaque jour. Les modules médicaux à la carte personnalisent votre application pour répondre au plus près à vos besoins spécifiques (prescription, téléexpertise, adressage, questionnaire patient, visioconférence) PandaLab est certifié HDS/ISO 27001, hébergé en France et garantit une stricte confidentialité de vos données, comme imposée par les normes en vigueur concernant les données de santé à caractère personnel. Restez branchés !

about: Hawai'i Land Trust (HILT) is Hawaiʻi’s islands-wide land trust that is both a Hawaiʻi 501(c)3 nonprofit, and a nationally accredited land trust. HILT formed in 2011 from a merger of four island land trusts on Maui, Oʻahu, Hawaiʻi Island, and Kauaʻi. A dedicated Board of Directors representing all major islands guides HILT, supported by a lean and hard working staff. HILT has protected over 21,500 acres across Hawaiʻi, through 7 public preserves owned and stewarded by HILT, 44 conservation easements protecting agricultural, ecological, and cultural resources on private lands, and 5 facilitated conservation transactions. We protect lands that are integral to Hawaiʻi’s well-being and character, upholding our kuleana to these lands, and the communities they are in, through thoughtful stewardship that deepens community connection to, and builds reciprocal relationships with, ʻāina.

about: Established in 2006, KAI Square is a high-tech company providing innovative technological solutions-related surveillance services & monitoring solutions. KAI Square has built a reputation within the Singapore surveillance market as a highly innovative and technically strong thought-leader who leading system integrators desire to work with. From a modest 7-men operation in 2006 to a strong 50-men operation today, KAI Square has been leading the trend in the Singapore security market with its state-of-the-art security systems by providing the KAI Square Unified Platform. KAI Square is well regarded as the next generation high-end technology provider to telecommunication companies, as well as system integrators. Adopting this proven business model and expertise which have been the key driving force behind the company's strong growth, KAI Square has a growing clientele that comprises of fleet operators, police force and business in the healthcare, security and logistics sector. It currently manages over 20,000 security cameras. Leveraging on its success in the local market, KAI Square sets to venture into the overseas market in 2010, by setting up marketing offices in Beijing, Tianjin, Bangkok and Taipei. KAI Square will continue to grow its global market presence by deploying its technology to seven new cities.
